==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Trey
<hw>Trey</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[OF. <ets>treis</ets>
three, F. <ets>trois</ets>, L. <ets>tres</ets>. See <er>Three</er>, and
cf. <er>Tray-trip</er>.]</ety> <def>Three, at cards, dice, or dominoes;
a card, die, or domino of three spots or pips.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Seven is my chance and thine is cinq and <qex>trey</qex>.</q>
<rj><qau>Chaucer.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Tri-</ent>⟦br⟧
